Tempo Run
## Warm-up
• 1500m easy at <PACE_ZONE_2_ENDURANCE>
• 4x100m strides progressing to <PACE_ZONE_3_TEMPO>

• 5000m steady tempo at <PACE_ZONE_3_TEMPO>

• Focus on consistent pacing and controlled breathing

• 1500m easy at <PACE_ZONE_2_ENDURANCE>

EMBED_STR:
Full Body Strength
## Warm-up
• 15 min dynamic movement and mobility

## Main Set
### Compound Movements
• Back Squats: 5 sets x 5 reps at 80-85% max
• Deadlifts: 4 sets x 6 reps at 75-80% max
• Bench Press: 4 sets x 8 reps
• Bent-Over Rows: 4 sets x 10 reps
• Overhead Press: 3 sets x 8 reps

### Accessory Work
• Core circuit: 3 rounds
• Plank variations: 3x60 seconds

## Cool-down
• 10 min stretching and mobility

**Tips:** Focus on form over weight. Rest 2-3 minutes between heavy sets.

EMBED_STR:
Full Body Strength
## Warm-up
• 15 min dynamic movement and mobility

## Main Set
### Compound Movements
• Back Squats: 5 sets x 5 reps at 80-85% max
• Deadlifts: 4 sets x 6 reps at 75-80% max
• Bench Press: 4 sets x 8 reps
• Bent-Over Rows: 4 sets x 10 reps
• Overhead Press: 3 sets x 8 reps

### Accessory Work
• Core circuit: 3 rounds
• Plank variations: 3x60 seconds

## Cool-down
• 10 min stretching and mobility

**Tips:** Focus on form over weight. Rest 2-3 minutes between heavy sets.

EMBED_STR:
Full Body Strength
## Warm-up
• 15 min dynamic movement and mobility

## Main Set
### Compound Movements
• Back Squats: 5 sets x 5 reps at 80-85% max
• Deadlifts: 4 sets x 6 reps at 75-80% max
• Bench Press: 4 sets x 8 reps
• Bent-Over Rows: 4 sets x 10 reps
• Overhead Press: 3 sets x 8 reps

### Accessory Work
• Core circuit: 3 rounds
• Plank variations: 3x60 seconds

## Cool-down
• 10 min stretching and mobility

**Tips:** Focus on form over weight. Rest 2-3 minutes between heavy sets.

EMBED_STR:
Hill Repeats - Power Development
## Warm-up
• 2000m easy running to hill location
• Dynamic leg swings and activation

## Main Set
### Hill Sprints
10 intervals of:
• 60-90 second hill sprint at maximum sustainable effort
• Focus on powerful drive from glutes and hamstrings
• Walk/jog back down for full recovery

## Cool-down
• 2000m easy running
• Extra stretching focus on calves and hip flexors

**Tips:** Hill repeats build power and running economy. Drive hard up the hill with good posture.

EMBED_STR:
Over-Under Intervals
## Warm-up
• 25 min progressive build
• Include several short efforts at threshold

## Main Set
### Over-Under Sets
4 intervals of:
• 2 min at 95% FTP (under threshold)
• 1 min at 105% FTP (over threshold)
• Repeat 4 times per interval (12 min total)
• 5 min recovery between intervals

## Cool-down
• 20 min easy spin

**Tips:** Over-unders teach you to manage surges in power while maintaining threshold effort.

EMBED_STR:
Over-Under Intervals
## Warm-up
• 25 min progressive build
• Include several short efforts at threshold

## Main Set
### Over-Under Sets
4 intervals of:
• 2 min at 95% FTP (under threshold)
• 1 min at 105% FTP (over threshold)
• Repeat 4 times per interval (12 min total)
• 5 min recovery between intervals

## Cool-down
• 20 min easy spin

**Tips:** Over-unders teach you to manage surges in power while maintaining threshold effort.

EMBED_STR:
Full Body Strength
## Warm-up
• 15 min dynamic movement and mobility

## Main Set
### Compound Movements
• Back Squats: 5 sets x 5 reps at 80-85% max
• Deadlifts: 4 sets x 6 reps at 75-80% max
• Bench Press: 4 sets x 8 reps
• Bent-Over Rows: 4 sets x 10 reps
• Overhead Press: 3 sets x 8 reps

### Accessory Work
• Core circuit: 3 rounds
• Plank variations: 3x60 seconds

## Cool-down
• 10 min stretching and mobility

**Tips:** Focus on form over weight. Rest 2-3 minutes between heavy sets.

EMBED_STR:
Full Body Strength
## Warm-up
• 15 min dynamic movement and mobility

## Main Set
### Compound Movements
• Back Squats: 5 sets x 5 reps at 80-85% max
• Deadlifts: 4 sets x 6 reps at 75-80% max
• Bench Press: 4 sets x 8 reps
• Bent-Over Rows: 4 sets x 10 reps
• Overhead Press: 3 sets x 8 reps

### Accessory Work
• Core circuit: 3 rounds
• Plank variations: 3x60 seconds

## Cool-down
• 10 min stretching and mobility

**Tips:** Focus on form over weight. Rest 2-3 minutes between heavy sets.

• Plank variations: 3x60 seconds

## Cool-down
• 10 min stretching and mobility

**Tips:** Focus on form over weight. Rest 2-3 minutes between heavy sets.

EMBED_STR:
Full Body Strength
## Warm-up
• 15 min dynamic movement and mobility

## Main Set
### Compound Movements
• Back Squats: 5 sets x 5 reps at 80-85% max
• Deadlifts: 4 sets x 6 reps at 75-80% max
• Bench Press: 4 sets x 8 reps
• Bent-Over Rows: 4 sets x 10 reps
• Overhead Press: 3 sets x 8 reps

### Accessory Work
• Core circuit: 3 rounds
• Plank variations: 3x60 seconds

## Cool-down
• 10 min stretching and mobility

**Tips:** Focus on form over weight. Rest 2-3 minutes between heavy sets.

## Warm-up
